text: Eunidia flavoapicata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939.BioLib.cz - Eunidia flavoapicata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Eunidia flavoapicata flavoapicata Breuning, 1939 * Eunidia flavoapicata tchadensis Lepesme & Breuning, 1955 ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1939
title: Eunidia flavoapicata
